//! `tsgo_execute`: the `tsc` program-build orchestration and CLI driver.
//!
//! Ports Go's `internal/execute` package (the `tsc.go` build/emit orchestration,
//! `--build` mode, watch loop, and the `cmd/tsgo` entry's command execution).
//! Skeleton crate registered ahead of P9; the build orchestration is filled in by
//! the P9 rounds.

//! `tsgo_ls_lsutil`: language-service utility helpers.
//!
//! Ports Go's `internal/ls/lsutil` package (shared language-service helpers used
//! by `ls/change`, `ls/autoimport`, `format`, and the `ls` root). Skeleton crate
//! registered ahead of P7; the helpers are filled in by the P7 rounds.

//! `tsgo_format`: the TypeScript formatter (formatting rules engine).
//!
//! Ports Go's `internal/format` package (the formatting rules engine, indentation,
//! and format-on-type/range/document entry points used by the language service).
//! Skeleton crate registered ahead of the P7 format round; the engine is filled in
//! by that round.

//! `tsgo`: the command-line entry point (ports Go's `cmd/tsgo/main.go`).
//!
//! Thin argv dispatcher that routes to the `tsgo_execute` `tsc` path (and, later,
//! the LSP server / API modes). Skeleton registered ahead of the P9 cmd round;
//! the dispatch is filled in by that round.

